snippet.title: Fun Fact Friday ft. Amber Laura | Marriage Boot Camp: Hip Hop Edition
snippet.description:
For this week's #FunFactFriday, WE're putting the spotlight on “Marriage Boot Camp: Hip Hop Edition” star, Amber Laura! Check it out.

#HipHopBootCamp #MarriageBootCamp 

Subscribe to the WE tv channel for more clips: https://goo.gl/1CiBkL

Four hip hop couples, including rap legend N.O.R.E., face the music at Marriage Boot Camp. Dr. Ish Major & Judge Lynn Toler help them confront lies, tears, and denials, but when dark secrets are exposed, will the relationships survive?
